Premier of KwaZulu-Natal, Sihle Zikalala briefs the media on the current status and relief efforts in the province. Courtesy #DStv403 DURBAN - KwaZulu Natal Premier Sihle Zikalala says they'll ask government to declare the floods a national disaster.
Zikalala says they have caused greater levels of devastation and that much more assistance will be required to help those affected.